RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2005-0331. Whitaker v. M.T. Automotive, Inc.

Summit App. No. 21836, 2004-0hio-7166. Reported at 111 Ohio St.3d 177, 2006-0hio-5481, 855 N.E.2d 825. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.
